  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study studies the prevalence between obstructive sleep apnea syndrome and sensorineural
      hearing loss. We recruit patients who have been treated for sudden sensorineural hearing loss
      in Poitiers' University Hospital between 2010 et 2017, and we detect if they have OSA with a
      ventilatory polygraphy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
